%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%% uminho/emed/schl-defaults.ldf
%% NOVA thesis configuration file
%%
%% Customization for EM-UMINHO (strings and cover)
